
mixin ColoredLinksExampleDescription
  p&attributes(attributes) You can use the 
    code .link-*
    |  classes to colorize links. Unlike the 
    a(href=`https://getbootstrap.com/docs/${bootstrapVersion}/helpers/colored-links/`)
      code .text-*
      |  classes
    | , these classes have a 
    code :hover
    |  and 
    code :focus
    |  state.

